stings) + Phase 5 (US2 - Browse Listings)\n\n### Week 2: Filtering + Reservations + Extension\n- Days 1-2: Phase 6 (US3 - Filtering) + Phase 7 (US4 - Alerts)\n- Days 3-4: Phase 8 (US5 - Reservations)\n- Days 5-6: Phase 9 (US7 - Navigation)\n- Day 7: Phase 10 (Polish)\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- [P] tasks can run in parallel (different files)\n- [Story] label maps task to user story for traceability\n- Commit after each task or logical group\n- Test each user story independently at checkpoint\n- Verify all grading criteria met before submission\n- Total: 100 tasks for 100 marks\n\n=== Operation 2 Result (Text) ===\n# Total entries: 16\n\nd androidTest Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\androidTest\nd test Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\test\nd java Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\androidTest\\java\nd java Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\test\\java\nd com Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\androidTest\\java\\com\nd com Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\test\\java\\com\nd accommodation Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\androidTest\\java\\com\\accommodation\nd accommodation Apr 21 17:13 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\test\\java\\com\\accommodation\nd main Apr 13 16:50 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\CSE24-180-MAD\\CSE24-180-MAD\\MAD Assignment\\app\\src\\main\nd res Apr 13 16:50 C:\\Users\\otsil\\OneDrive\\Documents\\Git